                                                    "name": "A Rose for Emily",
                                                    "notify": true,
                                                    "description": "I spoke to the ghost of Patrick Ratana today. He's trapped for eternity because he didn't give his sweetheart a rose. It would be nice if I could find a way to help him.",
                                                    "notes": ""
